user.biography: Healing through positive words, art and light. To buy click the link below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 24, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'We forget that waking up each day is the first thing we should be grateful for. Unknown'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 24, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'OK, FINE I'LL GO CAMPING'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 24, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'In the blink of an eye, everything can change. So forgive often and love with all your heart. Take no one for granted, for you never know what tomorrow will bring. Unknown'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 23, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, outdoors and text that says 'HERE'S THE TRUTH: YOUR SITUATION IS NEVER PERMANENT. IT's WHAT YOU MAKE IT. LIFE ISN'T SOLID, IT'S FLUID. It changes.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 23, 2021. May be an image of dog and text that says 'Family isn't always blood. It's the peoplε in youR life who want you in theirs. The onEs who accept you for who you arE. The onEs who would do anything to SEE you smile, and who lOve you no matter what.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'IF YOU ARE STRUGGLING TODAY, REMEMBER THIS: You have survived everything you've gone through up to this point. The best day of your life is still yet to come. There are still people you haven't met, and things you haven't experienced. YOU CAN DO THIS.'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A wise man said: Don't seek revenge. The rotten fruits will fall by themselves.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 21, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'DON'T WORRY ABOUT WHAT PEOPLE SAY BEHIND YOUR BACK. THEY ARE THE PEOPLE WHO ARE FINDING FAULTS IN YOUR LIFE INSTEAD OF FIXING THEIR OWN.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 21, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'When you least expect it, something great will come along. Something better than you ever planned for. Be patient. Be smart. Stay focused.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, sky and text that says 'WHEN WE LOSE SOMEONE WE LOVE, WE MUST LEARN NOT TO LIVE WITHOUT THEM, BUT TO LIVE WITH THE LOVE THEY LEFT BEHIND.'.

Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 20, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Be grateful and be positive, because life is too short to always be worried. Let go of the stress and realize you're blessed. P.T'.
Photo by Positive Thoughts on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The world is a reflection of you.'.
